00:27:38,000 --> 00:27:39,310
Look there.

568
00:27:44,880 --> 00:27:46,590
Something big is coming up ahead.

569
00:27:46,590 --> 00:27:47,480
Wait,

570
00:27:47,480 --> 00:27:48,990
