710
00:35:10,040 --> 00:35:11,780
Matches are for victory.

711
00:35:11,810 --> 00:35:13,010
Next time,

712
00:35:12,250 --> 00:35:13,160
[Football is for victory,
not for applause]

713
00:35:13,180 --> 00:35:14,020
[or for trophies, but to prove]

714
00:35:13,510 --> 00:35:14,630
