732
00:37:36,110 --> 00:37:37,030
Nonsense.

733
00:37:37,440 --> 00:37:38,670
I bought them to eat.

734
00:37:39,920 --> 00:37:40,760
Boss,

735
00:37:40,760 --> 00:37:43,690
