755
00:38:38,630 --> 00:38:40,430
Speed up your movement, Zhi Hui.

756
00:38:42,150 --> 00:38:43,330
♪ Lasting memories ♪

757
00:38:44,260 --> 00:38:48,580
♪ The distance
