765
00:39:08,610 --> 00:39:09,900
♪ Brilliant as stars ♪

766
00:39:11,520 --> 00:39:12,580
♪ Running towards you ♪

767
00:39:13,430 --> 00:39:14,540
♪ I keep moving fearlessly ♪

768
00:39:18,580 --> 00:39:19,490
♪ Walk side by side ♪

769
00:39:20,390 --> 00:39:22,030
